DaluriNewHoiroLines		0	$ 67	$ New Hoiro, it was the first city built here in E'Siraph. $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		1	$ 86	$ Named, of course, for the old city of Hoiro, where the first reaping ravaged. $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		2	$ 102	$ When this second reaping began, for a whole fortnight New Hoiro was beseiged by the reapers. $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		3	$ 75	$ At the end, the gates opened as the Queen of New Hoiro was slain. $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		4	$ 47	$ But opened not by the guards, no. $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		5	$ 92	$ It's only ever a matter of time before the ones hiding become reapers themselves. $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		6	$ 36	$ How long have I got? $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		7	$ 43	$ Don't know... $
DaluriNewHoiroLines		8	$ 58	$ Depends how long I can stay determined for. $

