DaluriWhatLines			10	$ 82	$ If it's blocked, you'll likely need to pass through Ixinik's Casting Lab. $
DaluriWhatLines			11	$ 80	$ Of course, you could always just hide away like I do... $
DaluriWhatLines			12	$ 51	$ It's safer, and life's longer that way. $

